imageDescription: A road map spread out on a wooden table. The map is old and worn, with many creases and tears. A red marker has been used to trace a route from one city to another. The route is long and winding, and it passes through many different towns and villages. A compass sits next to the map, and a magnifying glass rests on top of the route.
